OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FAutistic people and those with ADHD
OL,7,Fare avoiding seeking health care as
OL,8,Fthey can find waiting rooms
OL,9,F"unbearable", experts have said as
OL,10,Fthey called for more to be done to
OL,11,Fsupport neurodivergent people navigate
OL,12,FNHS services.
OL,14,FThe Society of Radiographers (SoR)
OL,15,Fsaid patients face a number of
OL,16,Fbarriers when accessing care ` from
OL,17,Fthe way they can communicate with
OL,18,Fhealth workers to overstimulating
OL,19,Fdiagnostic tools and waiting areas.
