OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FIt is also calling for more to be done
OL,7,Fto help staff who are neurodivergent,
OL,8,Fsaying that some workers are being
OL,9,F"driven out" of the NHS.
OL,11,FThe SoR has called on the health
OL,12,Fservice to introduce inclusive spaces,
OL,13,Fsuch as autism-friendly waiting rooms,
OL,14,Fand for better communication to make
OL,15,Fsure people's needs are being met.
