OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FBen Potts, a diagnostic radiographer
OL,7,Fwho is researching the experiences of
OL,8,Fneurodivergent patients, said:
OL,9,F"Research has shown that 51% of
OL,10,Fautistic people find waiting rooms
OL,11,Funbearable ` they're too much of a
OL,12,Fsensory experience ` that's compared
OL,13,Fwith 8% of non-autistic people.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
