OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,F"Going into an MRI scanner, which
OL,7,Fmakes a lot of noise, or into an X-ray
OL,8,Fexamination room, where radiographers
OL,9,Fneed to touch patients to position
OL,10,Fthem accurately for the X-ray imaging,
OL,11,Fthese are areas where there can be an
OL,12,Fextra layer of difficulty for autistic
OL,13,Fpeople."
OL,15,FMr Potts said that even getting help
OL,16,Fin the first place can be difficult,
OL,17,Fespecially if it involves a phone call.
OL,19,F"Some autistic people find phone calls
OL,20,Fvery, very difficult. So they won't
OL,21,Fmake the call," he said.
