OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FDr Julie Woodley, a senior lecturer in
OL,7,Fradiography at the University of the
OL,8,FWest of England, said neurodivergent
OL,9,Fclinicians working in the NHS can also
OL,10,Fface difficulties.
OL,12,F"A lot of managers seem unaware of how
OL,13,Fto manage staff on the neurodiversity
OL,14,Fspectrum, so staff don't feel
OL,15,Fsupported at all," she said.
OL,17,F"Some people have said that they've
OL,18,Fgot to the point where they're going
OL,19,Fto have to leave the NHS. They feel
OL,20,Fworn down by it all."
