OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FDean Rogers, executive director of
OL,7,Findustrial strategy and member
OL,8,Frelations at the SoR, said: "Hospitals
OL,9,Fcan be stressful and intimidating
OL,10,Fplaces for anyone to visit or work.
OL,12,F"This can lead to poor communication,
OL,13,Fwhich contributes to increased patient
OL,14,Frisk and inefficient treatment.
OL,16,F"These risks and costs are amplified
OL,17,Ffor patients and staff who are
OL,18,Fneurodivergent.
OL,26,@pD@]OUtD@AOUxD@AOU
