OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,F"There is encouraging research showing
OL,7,Fhow cost-effective neurodiversity-
OL,8,Fsensitive changes can improve
OL,9,Fproductivity and outcomes for all
OL,10,Fstaff and patients.
OL,12,F"These include autism-friendly waiting
OL,13,Fareas, simplified systems and patient-
OL,14,Fexperience videos."
OL,16,FThe SoR said national guidelines to
OL,17,Fhelp patients and staff are "urgently"
OL,18,Fneeded.
