OL,3,CNHS 'needs to do more to support
OL,4,Cautistic people'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for NHS England said:
OL,7,F"All patients, including those with
OL,8,Fneurodiversity, deserve the best
OL,9,Fpossible experience of NHS care ` and
OL,10,Fwe have rolled out mandatory training
OL,11,Fon learning disability and autism for
OL,12,Fall NHS staff.
OL,14,F"Our ADHD taskforce is also examining
OL,15,Fways NHS services can be improved to
OL,16,Freduce inequalities in care, and we
OL,17,Fhave issued updated guidance to
OL,18,Fimprove support for autistic people."
